           ----------------------
           The Tax Receipt Sample
           ----------------------

The Tax Receipt Sample

  The Tax Receipt sample demonstrates the behavior of a dynamic PDF form.\
  This form prints three copies of a tax receipt on a single page:
  the foundation’s copy, the chapter’s copy, and the income tax copy.\
  The sample includes these files:

*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|<<File>>                                       |<<Description>>                                               |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Tax Receipt.xdp}Tax Receipt.xdp}}           |LiveCycle Designer ES form file located in the Forms folder   |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Tax Receipt.xml}Tax Receipt.xml}}           |XML data files located in the Data folder                     |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Signature.tif}Signature.tif}}               |Image files located in the Images folder                      |
|{{{Tax Receipt.tif}Tax Receipt.tif}}           |                                                              |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Tax Receipt.pdf}Tax Receipt.pdf}}           |Rendered forms with merged data located in the Outputs folder |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+

  The transformation output:
  
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|<<File>>                                       |<<Description>>                                               |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Tax Receipt.xsl}Tax Receipt.xsl}}           |                                                              |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Tax Receipt.pdf}Tax Receipt.pdf}}           |                                                              |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Tax Receipt Ref.xsl}Tax Receipt Ref.xsl}}   |                                                              |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|{{{Tax Receipt Ref.pdf}Tax Receipt Ref.pdf}}   |                                                              |
*-----------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+

